Docs.summary: Represents a pair of annotation values in a scaffolded or hand-coded .
Docs.remarks: Code First allows for custom annotations to be associated with columns and tables in the generated model. This class represents a pair of annotation values in a migration such that when the Code First model changes the old annotation value and the new annotation value can be provided to the migration and used in SQL generation.
